    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade E46 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance. This example features the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, characterized by its six individual throttle bodies and high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. The dual-VANOS system has been fully overhauled, and preventative rod bearing replacement is documented. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential. The chassis is structurally flawless, featuring proactive subframe reinforcement and a refreshed suspension geometry with Bilstein B16 coilovers for surgical turn-in. Finished in original Carbon Black Metallic, the exterior remains in concours-level condition, free of common clear coat degradation or panel gaps.",
